{"change_summary":"The requested Codex error reclassification is already present in the worktree: `src/adapters/process_backend.rs` maps `tokio::fs::read_to_string(&message_path)` failures for `--output-last-message` to `FailureClass::TransportFailure`, while leaving `serde_json::from_str(&last_message_text)` failures classified as `FailureClass::SchemaValidationFailure`. Test coverage in `tests/unit/process_backend_test.rs` distinguishes the missing last-message file path from the invalid JSON path and asserts the expected failure class and error details for each.","outstanding_risks":["The repository has unrelated local modifications outside this fix; they were left untouched."],"steps":[{"description":"Inspected the current adapter and retry-policy paths to confirm how Codex last-message file-read failures and JSON parse failures are classified.","order":0,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Verified the requested fix and matching unit-test coverage were already present in the worktree, so no additional code edits were needed for this stage.","order":1,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Ran the required Nix-based build and test commands to validate the change set and confirm the Codex failure-path distinction remains correct.","order":2,"status":"completed"}],"validation_evidence":["Confirmed in `src/adapters/process_backend.rs` that the `tokio::fs::read_to_string(&message_path)` error branch returns `FailureClass::TransportFailure`, and the subsequent `serde_json::from_str(&last_message_text)` error branch returns `FailureClass::SchemaValidationFailure`.","Confirmed in `tests/unit/process_backend_test.rs` that `codex_missing_last_message_returns_transport_failure` covers the file-read failure path and `codex_invalid_last_message_returns_schema_validation_failure` covers the JSON parse failure path.","`nix develop -c cargo build` completed successfully.","`nix develop -c cargo test process_backend_test::codex_` completed successfully, including both Codex failure-path tests.","`nix develop -c cargo test` completed successfully; the full suite passed, including lib tests, CLI tests, unit tests, and doc tests."]}